'''Fibromyalgia''' is a very severe condition with chronic and extensive [[pain]]. The exact causes are not known. However, symptoms are not totally restricted to the pain. There are also sleep disturbances, joint stiffness and severe fatigue. The problem is sometimes comorbid with [[depression]], stress and [[anxiety]]. Fibromyalgia affects mostly women, though men can also be affected. Adults are usually victims, although [[child]]ren may also be affected.
